      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in solid, reliable condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure long-term performance. Mechanically, it is in great shape with a smooth engine and a transmission that shifts precisely; there are no known mechanical issues or leaks. The exterior paint retains a good shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, showing only light wear on the upholstery and touchpoints. All electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully operational, and the car comes with a complete service history.",
      "price": 34500.0,
