      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and still looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here. It's been kept in a climate-controlled garage and meticulously maintained. If you're looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 44500.0,
