    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector-tier condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The valvetrain has been meticulously serviced, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement using treated bearings for preventative longevity. Power is channeled through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that remains tight and responsive. Finished in pristine original paint with an immaculate interior, this vehicle exhibits zero deferred maintenance and optimal compression across all cylinders. A mechanically flawless example for the discerning enthusiast.",
